description: This is a market group over what Donald J. Trump will say during his rally in Coachella, California scheduled for October 12, 2024.

markets.description:
Donald Trump has scheduled a rally on October 12 in Coachella, California (see: https://event.donaldjtrump.com/events/president-donald-j-trump-to-hold-a-rally-in-coachella-california).

This market will resolve to "Yes" if Trump says "border" 20 or more times during their appearance at this event. Otherwise, the market will resolve to "No".

Any usage of the term regardless of context will count toward the resolution of this market.

Pluralization/possessive of the term will count toward the resolution of this market, however other forms will NOT count.

Compound words will count as long as "border" is part of the compound word and references the meaning which refers to a political boundary between nations.

If this candidate does not appear at this event, or if the event is otherwise cancelled or delayed beyond October 12, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source will be the video of the event.
markets.question: Will Trump say "border" 20 or more times during California rally on October 12?
